title: James Stewart - Two Rode Together - Richard Widmark (1961).avi
description:
Classic Western with Jimmy Stewart and Richard Widmark.  Very watchable movie.  Jimmy Stewart plays a very likeable, self realistic, unabashed rogue.  Richard Widmark is the solid Army lieutenant that he plays off of.

Full screen, appears to be a capture from a premium channel.  The quality of the file is very good.  An occasional logo display in the lower right corner, that is not too irritating.  I have not yet found a better file.

Avi format, no subs, english only.  It is posted here already in a different file format but there does not appear to be anyone seeding.  I&#039;ll seed according to my usual schedule.

The US Army is under pressure from the desperate relatives of white prisoners of the Comanches to secure their rescue. A cynical and corrupt marshal, Guthrie McCabe, is persuaded by an army lieutenant to assist in the negotiations with the Comanches. However, just two captives are released; and their reintegration into white society proves highly problematic
